-- Assurant Names Emerson’s Montupet to Join Insurer’s Board
-- B y   S u s a n n a   P a k
-- 2012-09-13T20:26:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-13/assurant-names-emerson-s-montupet-to-join-insurer-s-board.html
Assurant Inc. (AIZ) , the insurer of
foreclosed homes, named Jean-Paul Montupet to its board of
directors.  Montupet, 64, the chairman of Emerson Electric Co.’s
Industrial Automation business, will be on the insurer’s
Nominating and Corporate Governance Committee, New York-based
Assurant said today in a statement distributed by PR Newswire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Susanna Pak in New York at 
